error type.invalid-operator-operands: operator `+` is not defined for `Bool` and `Int`
  label 10..18: these operand types do not support this operator
  note: `+` accepts two numbers or two Text values
  note: dispatch is left-biased: `Bool` is the sole method owner; Aven does not fall back to `Int.+`
  note: reverse the operands only when doing so preserves the operation's intended semantics
